%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Cost+of+Moral+Leadership%3A+The+Spirituality+of+Dietrich+Bonhoeffer&amp;rft.pub=William+B.+Eerdmans+Publishing&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.isbn=0802805116&amp;rft.au=Kelly%2C+Geffrey+B.&amp;rft.au=F.+Burton+Nelson&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEthics+%28Bonhoeffer%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite id=\"CITEREFMetaxas2015\" class=\"citation book\">Metaxas, Eric (2015). <i>Bonhoeffer Student Edition: Pastor, Martyr, Prophet, Spy</i>. Thomas Nelson. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0718022440\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0718022440\">0718022440</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Bonhoeffer+Student+Edition%3A+Pastor%2C+Martyr%2C+Prophet%2C+Spy&amp;rft.pub=Thomas+Nelson&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.isbn=0718022440&amp;rft.au=Metaxas%2C+Eric&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEthics+%28Bonhoeffer%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite id=\"CITEREFMuers2007\" class=\"citation journal\">Muers, Rachel (2007).  Jackie Leach Scully, Pink Dandelion, eds. \"<span style=\"padding-left:0.2em;\">'</span>It is Worse to Be Evil Than to Do Evil': Dietrich Bonhoeffer's Challenge to the Quaker Conscience\". <i>Good and Evil: Quaker Perspectives</i>. Ashgate Publishing. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0754656217\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0754656217\">0754656217</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Good+and+Evil%3A+Quaker+Perspectives&amp;rft.atitle=%27It+is+Worse+to+Be+Evil+Than